        <title>PP.PHONE.CONFIRMATIONS</title>
        <table>PP.PHONE.CONFIRMATIONS</table>
    </header>
    <overview>
        <ovdesc>
            <p>The information which are related to the phone delivery method are stored in this table.The operator will have an access to this table and can send out confirmations accordingly.</p>
        </ovdesc>
    </overview>
    <menu>
        <t>
            <field>DebitMainAccountCurrencyCode</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Specifies the DebitMainAccount CurrencyCode from the payment order.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>Validation Rules :</p>
                <p>1. 3 characters</p>
                <p/>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>FTNumber</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Denotes the unique ID generated by the payments hub upon generating a payment order.</p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
                <p>16 alphanumeric characters.</p>
                <p/>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>ID</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Indicates the unique ID generated by the Payments Hub.</p>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>OldID</field>
            <desc>
