                <p>Specifies the confirmation Sequence number of the Payment Order.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>Validation Rules :</p>
                <p>1. 1-7 Numeric characters</p>
                <p/>
            </desc>
        </t>
        <t>
            <field>Action</field>
            <desc>
                <p>Used for internal purpose. Value of this field determines values of fields, 'RAC' and 'RSC'</p>
                <p>Possible values:</p>
                <p>N - New</p>
                <p>M - Modified </p>
                <p>R -  Reverse</p>
                <p>This field can hold upto 1 alphanumeric character and the value is not editable by the user.</p>
                <p/>
            </desc>
        </t>
